
==============================================================================
                                STEPS TO RUN ROUTER GLS
==============================================================================


	1. Take a new fresh xterm with clean environment
        2. clone ip-sbr repo
        3. cd ip-sbr
        4. setenv SBR_ROOT $cwd
        5. uncomment GLS lines in unsupported/export/data/xml/block_setup.tcl (lines 37 to 40) to uniquify the modules
        6. uncomment GLS lines in unsupported/export/data/xml/block_setup_febe.tcl (lines 28 to 31) to uniquify the modules

        7. ./unsupported/scripts/sbr_gls_regress synth ""                    #for all the configs

           (or)

           ./unsupported/scripts/sbr_gls_regress synth tgp_17ww49            #for single config

        8. ./unsupported/scripts/sbr_gls_regress synth "" noexec             # all the configs with no execution

            (or)

           ./unsupported/scripts/sbr_gls_regress synth tgp_17ww49 noexec     # single config with noexection

        To run GLS for a new config which is not in the  TaskConfig.sb.sbr.be.pl, hack the configs for now.         
